&lt;h2 id=&#34;model-with-a-local-interpretation&#34;&gt;Model with a local interpretation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The second model requires to introduces 3 additional variables.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#8f5902;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;// additional variables: the carries
